            <cc>            <div id="post_content_24789013748" class="d_post_content j_d_post_content ">            “<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62/KL8XnSVblN5GozPCJgUajgR7rQLZ7T+3pfKJtUWCTh9ssyDK1SDlnhDg47fRGLxIC1WNLHU2MljwrjhG0RrIyExmB9N/65I="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'黄金大米'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">黄金大米</a>事件”已过去月余，公众的愤怒其实冤枉了黄金大米这一造福发展中国家穷人的科研成果，也体现出对以儿童为样本进行医学研究的误解。而有关部门在这一事件中的表现，也足以再次引起我们对科学与监管的反思。<br><br><br>自从“国外科研机构利用中国儿童做转基因<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62/KL8XnSVblN5GozPCJgUajgR7rQLZ7T+3pfKJtUWCTh9ssyDK1SDlnhDg47fRGLxIC1WNLHU2MljwrjhG0RrIyExmB9N/65I="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'黄金大米'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">黄金大米</a>人体试验”这一消息在8月底在网上爆出后，舆论哗然，群情激动，即便事情过去已有月余，事件相关责任人之一也受到了停职处罚，在<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw63vsEfg+B3BHfoca777k7tpt6XyibVFgk4fbLMgytUg5Z4Q4OO30Ri8SAtVjSx1NjJY8K44RtEayMhMZgfTf+uS"  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'微博'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">微博</a>上仍不时有人提起此事。<br>然而，公众对此事中暴露出的科研试验管理乏术的愤怒，却着实冤枉了<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62/KL8XnSVblN5GozPCJgUajgR7rQLZ7T+3pfKJtUWCTh9ssyDK1SDlnhDg47fRGLxIC1WNLHU2MljwrjhG0RrIyExmB9N/65I="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'黄金大米'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">黄金大米</a>这一造福发展中国家穷人的科研成果，也体现出对以儿童为样本进行医学研究的误解。而有关部门在这一事件中的表现，也足以再次引起我们对科学与监管的反思。<br>一、<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62/KL8XnSVblN5GozPCJgUajgR7rQLZ7T+3pfKJtUWCTh9ssyDK1SDlnhDg47fRGLxIC1WNLHU2MljwrjhG0RrIyExmB9N/65I="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'黄金大米'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">黄金大米</a>真相<br><a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62/KL8XnSVblN5GozPCJgUajgR7rQLZ7T+3pfKJtUWCTh9ssyDK1SDlnhDg47fRGLxIC1WNLHU2MljwrjhG0RrIyExmB9N/65I="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'黄金大米'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">黄金大米</a>的研发始于科学家们不断地探索利用科学造福穷人的努力。它所要解决的问题是如何以低成本、便捷的方式克服不同程度的<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62VpgSFEDCOp/QjEZZt7NrJYbydX+yZRmtQIVBbKMq+e2pP27Lpz57Wzd6j1cz6QFRokZqq2rtY7Oddwueiheu5AG+4Cm4FSU0="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'维生素A'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">维生素A</a>缺乏症。<br>据<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw60OxUJqnAz0NqLjHe8EvK8gf8e+eH2uQ2RAl5x8raY3Rrel8om1RYJOH2yzIMrVIOWeEODjt9EYvEgLVY0sdTYyWPCuOEbRGsjITGYH03/rkg=="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'世界卫生组织'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">世界卫生组织</a>报告，全世界估计有 1.9 亿儿童和 1900 万孕妇患有不同程度的<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62VpgSFEDCOp/QjEZZt7NrJYbydX+yZRmtQIVBbKMq+e2pP27Lpz57Wzd6j1cz6QFRokZqq2rtY7Oddwueiheu5AG+4Cm4FSU0="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'维生素A'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">维生素A</a>缺乏症（VAD），每年发展中国家有 35 万儿童因 VAD 而失明，67 万儿童因 VAD 导致<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62WDRLTxJO1ecQdzKpDIOmhbkS5KpOyT9wiY65SX2hsh16xSq+FxHP6FdK7DP1v3oStqBaZnWN6vVdC7Gg5eFCxRzIfMQkPO5sAb7gKbgVJTQ=="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_wo