bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw61MjhblvLIgRfW7OlDoSB9dImOuUl9obIdesUqvhcRz+hXSuwz9b96EragWmZ1jer1XQuxoOXhQsUcyHzEJDzubAG+4Cm4FSU0="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'胡萝卜'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">胡萝卜</a>在内的多种水果蔬菜中都含能转化为维生素A的<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw61MjhblvLIgRfW7OlDoSB9dG+mG3MWFYIC3pfKJtUWCTh9ssyDK1SDlnhDg47fRGLxIC1WNLHU2MljwrjhG0RrIyExmB9N/65I="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'胡萝卜素'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">胡萝卜素</a>，但目前许多贫困地区人们能吃饱肚子就不错了，很难吃得上肉类和果蔬，也无法获得廉价的维生素A胶囊。几经探索，科学家们想到了通过转基因的手段，培育出富含维生素A的作物来。<br>从 2000 年初开始，经过反复努力，科学家们将<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62VpgSFEDCOp/QjEZZt7NrJYbydX+yZRmtQIVBbKMq+e2pP27Lpz57Wzd6j1cz6QFRokZqq2rtY7Oddwueiheu5AG+4Cm4FSU0="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'维生素A'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">维生素A</a>合成的前体—<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw63deYeYtdjFcZ8PIFcyz1pVvzr20ulkTjgiY65SX2hsh16xSq+FxHP6FdK7DP1v3oStqBaZnWN6vVdC7Gg5eFCxRzIfMQkPO5sAb7gKbgVJTQ=="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'β-胡萝卜素'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">β-胡萝卜素</a>的基因导入了<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw6227hspu0CaUpeHT5GNulSat6XyibVFgk4fbLMgytUg5Z4Q4OO30Ri8SAtVjSx1NjJY8K44RtEayMhMZgfTf+uS"  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'水稻'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">水稻</a>，这些基因的产物能够在<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw61+bBX0ojJzB44Ee60C2e0/t6X